data.description: Welcome to paradise in this updated, move-in ready 3/2/2 POOL home. Granite/Quartz kitchen w/ wood cabinets & dovetail drawers, plantation shutters, wood-like tile floors, updated bathrooms, split plan, high ceilings, beautiful French Silver Gem coat saltwater/heated pool w/ a tropical paradise of a yard....this one has it all. New roof (2022), new water heater (2023), refrigerator (2020), full set hurricane shutters, fully fenced, fresh paint, custom landscaping, full irrigation system on separate well, county water/sewer, open great room design and low HOA fees. Hurry this one will not last!
